                                          "gid":  "1823191198603877",
                                          "title":  "\"Black Myth: Wukong\" 25% Off Sale Incoming",
                                          "url":  "https://steamstore-a.akamaihd.net/news/externalpost/steam_community_announcements/1823191198603877",
                                          "is_external_url":  true,
                                          "author":  "xichen.huang",
                                          "contents":  "Happy New Year to all Destined Ones!\n\nAs the Chinese Year of the Horse arrives, the development team has prepared a limited-time festive offer. All editions (Standard, Digital Deluxe, and Deluxe Edition Upgrade) will soon be available at 25% off.\n\nThe specific schedule for Steam is as follows: [b]10 Feb, 02:00 – 24 Feb, 02:00 (Beijing Time)[/b]\n\nFor more details, please check the announcement on our [url=https://gamesci.cn/wukong/news/detail?id=269]official website[/url].\n\nThank you all for your company and support. May you brave frost and snow unscathed, safe and sound all year round.",
